selectedCommunities.name: Digital Artists' Space Singapore
selectedCommunities.description:
A wholesome community for Singapore-based digital artists to share their work (Open to digital artists at any skill level, with any art style).

Making digital art and getting your work out there is hella hard in Singapore especially when you are doing it alone. The international art groups out there are too huge, and the algorithm doesn't help! With this platform, we want to form an inclusive digital art community of Singapore-based digital artists (at any skill level) so that these artists can surround themselves with other artists and promote some healthy competition. 

SO LET'S MAKE SOME ART, POST THEM, & SOME FRIENDS HERE! Remember to be respectful of one another!


Posting Guidelines:

 ‚Ä¢ Introduction 
Artworks without captions are accepted, however, we strongly suggest the artist give a self-introductory message and brief explanation on the artwork they‚Äôre sharing, just to keep the community more lively.

 ‚Ä¢ Types of Digital Art
Digital art refers to digital paintings, photo manipulations, CGI, animation, 3D modelling and a mix of the aforementioned. 
 
 ‚Ä¢ CREDIT the Artist
Art studies are allowed, but you will have to credit the artist you are copying from. Tracing someone else's work immediately falls into this category.

‚Ä¢ NO EXPLICIT CONTENT
Follow the Facebook community standard of conduct. 
Nudity: https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/adult_nudity_sexual_activity
Violence: https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/graphic_violence
Hate Speech: https://www.facebook.com/communitystandards/hate_speech

‚Ä¢ Commissions & Promotion
You are allowed to post links of your portfolios, commissions, IGs, art-sites, along with an image/artwork of yours. Please handle commission transactions outside of the group.

‚Ä¢ 3 posts a day
Each member is only allowed to post 3 artworks/day.


General Guidelines:

 >>    DOS    <<

‚Ä¢ Constructive Criticism
Inputs and/or give constructive criticism that can help with the person‚Äôs work.
 
 ‚Ä¢ Support System
Try to make friends with each other! It‚Äôs great to get to know each other. Share, like and comment on posts to show your support! If you take things offline, remember to keep things safe!

‚Ä¢ Invite!
 Invite your SG-based digital artist friends!


>>    DON‚ÄôTs    <<

‚Ä¢ NO BULLYING/ HARRASSING/ BASHING
No form of bullying, harassment or bashing is allowed. Constructive criticism is allowed though. **SARCASM/TROLLING IS NOT CONSTRUCTIVE**

‚Ä¢ NO POSTING OF SENSITIVE/PROVOKING TOPICS/HATE SPEECHES
Art that attacks/insults/provokes any particular community (e.g. race, ethnicity, national origin, religious affiliation, sexual orientation, caste, sex, gender, gender identity, and serious disease or disability) are STRICTLY NOT ALLOWED.

‚Ä¢ NO SPAMMING
Do not post irrelevant things to the art group ‚Äì keep the community clean and toxic-free. 

‚Ä¢ NO EXPLICIT CONTENT 
Again, please keep this platform respectful and follow Facebook regulations.

‚Ä¢ NO STEALING OTHER ARTIST'S ART!!!!
